data.description: Owners have taken care of this property and are ready for their next adventure. Property was updated in 2020 with windows, drywall, paint, flooring, siding, pretty much the entire home. Ac unit replaced recently. Appliances are all newish and working condition. Bathrooms were also remodeled in 2020. Come and enjoy the gazebo and deck in the  generous size backyard. 4 bedrooms with split floor plan and plenty of updates throughout. Come and take a look!
